snippet.title: Chef Life: A Restaurant Simulator | Commented Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Create and manage your dream restaurant! Menus, purchasing, décor, staff, equipment, customers… and don't forget the actual cooking! Experience the daily life of a restaurateur and earn your awards from the MICHELIN Guide.

Chef Life: A Restaurant Simulator will be available February 2, 2023 on PC, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch.

Follow Chef Life on social media to never miss a thing!
